org.eclipse.emf.facet.custom.metamodel.v0_2_0.custom

Interface EClassCustomization

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DocumentedElement, Facet

    public interface EClassCustomization
extends Facet
    A representation of the model object 'EClass Customization'. An EClassCustomization contains the customization for an EClass. There must not exist two EClassCustomizations customizing the same EClass in the same customization.
